    "title": "Principal Radiologist at Suven Pharmaceuticals",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Radiologist looking for your next big career move? Suven Pharmaceuticals in Thane offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Suven Pharmaceuticals:\nSuven Pharmaceuticals is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Suven Pharmaceuticals!",
